RQ260Sort is a BusinessClass
    owned by rq
    prefix is W4962

    Patterns
        disable StaticTranslations
        implements WorkFile

    Persistent Fields
        WorkFile                is UniqueID
        WorkFileSeq             is Numeric size 12
        RqhRequester            is like Requester    
        RlnCompany              is like InventoryCompany
        RlnReqNumber            is like Requisition
        RlnLineNbr              is like LineNumber
        RlnItem                 is like Item
        RlnItemType             is like ItemType
        RlnServiceCode          is like ServiceCode
        RlnDescription          is like Description
        RlnQuantity             is like Quantity
        RlnEnteredUom           is like UnitOfMeasure   
        RlnUnitCost             is like InternationalCost
        RlnCostOption           is like CostOption
        RlnContract             is like Contract
        RlnVendor               is like Vendor
        RlnPurchFrLoc           is like VendorLocation  
        RlnPurchMajor           is like MajorPurchasingClass
        RlnPurchMinor           is like MinorPurchasingClass
        RlnBuyer                is like Buyer
        RlnFromCompany          is like Company   
        RlnFromLocation         is like InventoryLocation
        RlnReqLocation          is like RequestingLocation  
        RlnCreationDate         is Date    
        RlnPoCode               is like POCode   
        RlnVenItem              is like VendorItem    
        RlnStatus               is Numeric size 1
        RqhStatus               is Numeric size 1
        RlnClosedFl             is Boolean 
        RlnManufCode            is like ManufacturerCode  
        RlnManufDivision        is like ManufacturerDivision  
        RlnManufNbr             is like ManufacturerNumber  
        RlnEnteredItem          is like EnteredItem 
        RlnCostCd               is like CostCode
        RlnEntryFl              is like ItemEntryMethod 
        RlnApprovedFl           is Boolean 
        RlnRqSource             is like RqSource 
        RlnCommodityCode        is like CommCodes
        RlnPvnObjId             is like ObjId
        RlnGtin                 is like ItemGTIN

    Sets

        InsertionOrderSet
            indexed
            no duplicates
            primary
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                WorkFileSeq

        RQ260SortRQ260Sort1
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                RlnCompany
                RlnItem
                RlnVendor
                RlnReqLocation
                RlnReqNumber

        RQ260SortRQ260Sort2
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                RlnCompany
                RlnItem
                RlnReqLocation
                RqhRequester
                RlnReqNumber

        RQ260SortRQ260Sort3
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                RlnCompany
                RlnReqLocation
                RqhRequester
                RlnItem
                RlnReqNumber

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

            Field Rules
                WorkFileSeq
                    autosequence

        Delete is a Delete Action

        DeleteAll is a Set Action
            restricted

            Parameters
                WorkFileHeader is UniqueID

            Instance Selection
                where (WorkFile = WorkFileHeader)

            Local Fields
                LWorkFileHeader is a WorkFile

            Parameter Rules
                WorkFileHeader
                    required
                    LWorkFileHeader = WorkFileHeader

            Action Rules
                Instance Rules
                    invoke Delete

                Empty Set Rules
                    invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader

                Set Rules
                    Exit Rules
                        invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader
